room_title: Escape room "E.T. Extra Toppings" by Escapeocity in Chicago
room_description: You and your group have a reservation tonight at Area 50-Yum, an alien-themed pizza restaurant in town. When you get there, your waiter pulls you aside and tells you that they think something...strange is going on there. Luckily, their manager is going to be gone for an hour! Can you uncover the government conspiracy at Area 50-Yum before your hour is up and you all get caught?
